title: District Unknown - Ispandi Bootleg
description:
Psychedelic Metal from Kabul, Afghanistan


District Unknown was founded when brothers Qasem and Pedram met Qais and Lemar through their mutual friend guitarist/filmmaker Travis Beard in their home town of Kabul, Afghanistan. Both duos had been eager to create a new kind of metal sound, beginning with Doom Death Metal and Thrash and soon crafting Psychedelic Metal.

This Bootleg is a collection of all District Unknown's available songs from their Soundcloud account. All songs on the Bootleg were recorded (or at least uploaded) in 2012. This collection was made in hopes the band's music will be heard.
